Microsoft has announced that it will offer a big discount on the Xbox One X for Black Friday 2018. Its Black Friday sale will take place from 18-26 November, with the Xbox One X selling for $400. This is the “lowest price ever”, it said. Microsoft will also offer $100 off its Xbox One S Minecraft bundle. $70 off other bundles will also be available, and all deals comes with a digital copy of Gears of War 4. The company added that a range of games will be on sale, too. This includes Forza Horizon 4, Forza Motorsport 7, and PUBG. “This holiday is the perfect time to jump in, whether you already have an Xbox or are buying one for the first time,” said Microsoft.